PUSH DOCUMENT `1`
INVOKE $list WITH PARAMETER
LOAD VARIABLE $disk
INVOKE $addItem WITH 2 PARAMETERS
EXECUTE $push ON TARGET WITH PARAMETERS
STORE VARIABLE $_result_

3.EvaluateStatement:
